LGTM

Hi @newyyshan ,

can you submit same pr to branch-2.7

> Hi @newyyshan ,
> 
> can you submit same pr to branch-2.7

Thanks for your suggestion. I have submitted the code to  branch-2.7. For details, see: https://github.com/apache/ambari/pull/3062

> The changes look fine, but wouldn't it be better to either:
> 
> 1. all inherit from `ambari-project` or
> 2. Define the version once and simply reference it?

Agree with you. If you are fine, can I work on it as part of this PR only?

Oh, the dependency versions are already used internally in many pom but since ambari-metrics, ambari-logsearch etc are sub-projects of ambari in branch-2.7(unlike trunk), they have been provided with versions for each sub-project. For trunk PR #3067 it is defined only in ambari-project
